Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless pirates fight\Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure left behind\Nby Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body\Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,also takes to the sea\Nto become the next Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As Luffy and his friends\Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the World Government is less and less\Nable to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What adventure is waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After being separated from his friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy comes to rescue his brother Ace--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,who has been captured by the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,by sneaking into Impel Down - the \Ngreatest prison in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After running into Buggy on Level 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy went on to Level 2, the Demonic Beast Floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,where he joined up with Mr. 3 \N- a former Baroque Works agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and together, they all \Nheaded to the lower floors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there's a lot of fun \Ngoing on in the outside world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe, Fire Fist, just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there are dozens and dozens of silver \Nmedalists in the world who in the end didn't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...against Whitebeard and Roger \Nall holding back their tears.
