Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Monitor room! We are at the scene on Level 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see the image?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Keep us updated!
