Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.37,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:04.15,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,This hole is big enough for even \Nthe Sphinx to fall through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Straw Hat Luffy want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The prisoners on Level 2 are all \Nfree! How did they get the keys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they responsible for this, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guards are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it for Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Level 2 reporting! We need backup, pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The prisoners are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Send Blugori to Level 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just received word of \NStraw Hat Luffy's intent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?! From whom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku at \Nthe Headquarters sent word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The invader - Monkey D. Luffy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...the condemned prisoner - Portgas D. Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,those two are brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he came here to rescue Fire Fist Ace \Nbefore the public execution?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains why he keeps going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We were focused on Whitebeard's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If he pulls this off, the \Ntide will turn against us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Inform Warden Magellan at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And get the riot on Level 2 under control!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:59.06,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, Garp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're standing at a crossroads that \Ncould change the whole world of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but he keeps causing problems, \None after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That symbol represents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...the unity of over 170 member nations \Nin the four seas and the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which is to say - the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, do you realize how big the \Norganization that is after her is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know the enemies Robin has.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot the flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My new weapon - The giant \Nslingshot called "Kabuto"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure-Kill! Fire Bird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the time with the Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You annoy me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this has been unprecedented!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he's meddling with a prison where \Nno-one's escaped for 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the abhorrent Golden Lion,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a prison which has never been breached,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,known for so long as a robust  and \Niron-tight great fortress - Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He has disgraced its name by being \Nthe first to penetrate its walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he be your grandson, Garp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure has accomplished a \Nlot! I'm proud of my grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Bartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he took care of the \NStraw Hats at Sabaody Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that he was lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't going to trust the \Nword of a Warlord, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I wonder how he got through \Nthe Navy's impregnable defenses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he just flew in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap! If you weren't \Nknown as the hero of the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have made you take full \Nresponsibility for your family, Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take this old man's life but the \Nsituation is far more serious than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This has all been \Nthe Navy's blundering!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize how much Tsuru and I \Nworked to deal with the aftermath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's mine! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!  This floor is like a frying pan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we in the desert?! It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Level 3! Oh, I never wanted to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! I'm doomed along with you, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Looks like the lion's taking a cat nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is especially difficult \Nfor me and my wax powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't stand here for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do we have to walk \Nuntil we get somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chatting won't do anything but waste energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Grilled chicken is served!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hummingbird that fluttered down \Nfrom upstairs and got grilled in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How hot is it in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cooked perfectly! Yum-yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer the lion from \Nupstairs be barbecued.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to eat an animal \Nthat speaks like a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you have an appetite \Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There are some cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? It's a prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can hide from the sun in there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's definitely cooler than outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! You're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. 3, you better make some keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place to hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can we just get in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a miserable sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Prisoners on this floor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,were once all tough \Ncriminals with more than 50-million-berry bounties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The heat from the Inferno Hell underneath...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...along with depriving them of food \Nand water has made them half dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Level 3 - the Starvation Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:14:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know why this floor \Nis covered with sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chances are the sand that \Nyou're stepping on now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is the remains of a \Nprisoner who has dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stay here too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we will become like them before we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get away from here while \Nwe still have sweat to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Level 4 in hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, not that way! We gotta \Ntake the stairs on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--No, we should take the pass on the right.\N--Stop confusing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The targets are proceeding to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Just keep watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been able to \Ncontact Warden Magellan yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--Not yet!\N--What about the Blugori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They headed off to catch the \Ninvaders with their commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! The security of Impel Down \Nshouldn't fall to pieces this easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...are we back where we started from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we went in a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit being so relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that we should go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we make it to Level 4 soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--I told you "I'm not going!"\N--I told you "I'm not going!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to guide me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that we were \Ngonna save Ace together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop imagining things as you want them to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you would?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They are in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, draw the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on my own then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's a trap! They got us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made of iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't use my Chop-Chop Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it contains Sea Prism Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna torture us for \Nattempting to break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're goners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the invader - Straw \NHat Luffy and two others!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--What do you mean "two others?!"\N--Don't antagonize them, Buggy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damnit! I gotta rip this net!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are guards and Blugori here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,--Put the Sea Prism Stone handcuffs on them!\N--Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Saldeath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cell death? You don't look that old though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Saldeath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're a monkey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Get it right! It's my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:54.85,Sign,,0,0,411,,{\blur0.8\fad(0,550)\fs50\bord2.4\c&H000000&\t(6800,6845,\1a&HFF&)}Chief Guard\N{\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fs66\bord2.8}Saldeath
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.50,0:17:54.85,Sign,,0,0,411,,{\blur0.8\fad(0,550)\fs50\bord0\4a&HFF&}Chief Guard\N{\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fs66\bord0}Saldeath
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:54.85,Sign,,0,0,48,,{\blur0.8\fad(0,550)\fs50\bord2.4\c&H000000&\t(6800,6845,\1a&HFF&)}[Blugori Commander]
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.50,0:17:54.85,Sign,,0,0,48,,{\blur0.8\fad(0,550)\fs50\bord0\4a&HFF&}[Blugori Commander]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's no use holding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no place to get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...in this closed underwater prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lucky you were caught by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there are four Jailer Beasts \Nprowling around on the floors beyond this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! I don't wanna \Nface them and the warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we have gone the right way there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. We were watching you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but no matter which way you choose, \Nyou would have ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that how it was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Vongole bianco!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pasta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Soup spaghetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's onto pasta now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get squashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,--Spaghetti!\N--The Sphinx is awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, he's gonna break the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let those three, \Nespecially Straw Hat get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep-fried noodle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Noodles, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've been going through a phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great! Now, we can run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Mr. 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move quickly due to this heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They climbed up the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see Ace, tell him \Nthat I said "hello" and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"let's have a drink if I \Never see you again alive!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good little live bait for us, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy to see you were \Nalright but... Alright! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! How sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! It's heartbreaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay sharp! He is a pirate with \Na 300-million-berry price!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is our chance to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to fight you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Buckwheat noodle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! He's still around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna run! Chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the stairs to go down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll soon arrive at Fire Fist Ace's floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally. It took a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That floor is filled with notorious criminals from \Nall over,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,not just Fire Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not the place one can enter casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing this as a favor for a Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to grant it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, there is a prisoner \Nwho was once a Warlord like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry. I \Njust want to see Fire Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do anything improper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You better keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be safe here! They're \Nafter Straw Hat as we wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They closed up the staircase going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already too much for me to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Un, deux, faint!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Un, deux, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Un, deux, faint!\N--Who's singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Un, deux, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Un, deux, faint!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Un, deux, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.86,0:22:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this world is \Nabout a man and a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you're queer, \Nyou're a little of both!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The queer way is the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The queer way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The queer way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The queer waaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Impel Down beefs up security \Nafter its series of incidents,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.26,0:23:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,sealing the only way in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and the others are \Ncompletely trapped inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Unaware of the dilemma he's in, \NLuffy continues toward Ace's floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and unexpectedly encounters \Nan old friend along the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Unleashed Swan!\NA Reunion With Bon Clay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
